data.description: Westside home nestled in Saddlewood Ranch, features open living spaces, wood burning fireplace, ceramic tile flooring, several linen, coat and storage closets, mature vegetation at front and backyard, major plus with an additional covered area to the west side of the home, as well as a covered back patio for you to enjoy the lovely fall outdoor Arizona weather.  The location is conveniently located to amenities, I-10, West Saguaro National Park hikes and trails. No HOA with city views from the front of the home!
